    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An ornament especially found in woodwork and furniture consisting of a panel with a motif resembling a piece of linen laid in vertical folds.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
